	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a lvl 10 Barbarian BeastLord. I prefer being a &quot;good&quot; race and i am familiar with BlackBurrow so this was an easy choice for me.<br><br>Also i dont see many Barbarian Beastlords on my server ( almost all Vahshir) So I like being unique.<br><br>As far as weapons I was given a nice 1hb with wis stats so i used 1hb till lvl 9 and then picked up a polised steel ulak ( 100pp )so i have switched to that to bring my hand to hand up. Once i get dual wield I will probably use mace in primary and ulak in secondary. I am leaning more towards the &quot;Shaman&quot; side of my BeastL but wear a combo of wu's and wis gear. (With an ulthork helmet for the cool graphic.)<br>So basically im saying .. at early levels use the best weapon you can get. At least that's what i'd do.<br><br><br>Once I hit 10 I ran from Black burrow to NK and ported to Moon. Then i got an invis and ran thru Paludal till I found an Dk blue tunnel and camped there. Paludal is the best exp in the game at 10-25 so ill be here for a while.<br><br>Im looking forward to seeing my Dog get bigger.. right now looks like a stray that wont stop following me he he <br><br>Lucanor<br>barbarian beastlord<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Hobenroby<br>Halfling Druid<br>Cazic Thule</td></tr>
